<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 15:15:55 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title>周末象征图</title><link>https://some.pics/69eb8928dc07a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;周末结束（象征性图片）&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="An almost empty paper cup, with just a small amount of café latte left inside, traces of foam clinging to the inside of the cup. It is sunny, and the cup sits on a brown table. The image symbolises the amount of energy left, at the end of a long week. " height="3556" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/roteskuffen/69eb8928dc07a.jpg" width="3000"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://roteskuffen.some.pics"&gt;@roteskuffen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 15:15:55 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>自由里程</title><link>https://some.pics/69eb87a430ad9</link><description>&lt;p&gt;自由里程&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Car speedometer shows zero MPH with odometer reading 111,776 miles. Blue background with white numbers and symbols indicating seatbelt reminders." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/itsbrian/69eb87a430ad9.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://itsbrian.some.pics"&gt;@itsbrian&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 15:09:28 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>阳光下的惬意时光</title><link>https://some.pics/69eb81aac656a</link><description>&lt;p&gt;🏃🏻 尽情享受幸福。☀️🙌🏻&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="🏃🏻 Zalig genieten. ☀️🙌🏻" height="1486" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/atog/69eb81aac656a.jpg" width="1179"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://atog.some.pics"&gt;@atog&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Apr 2026 14:43:58 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>18度晴好天气</title><link>https://some.pics/69eb6